---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Demos">
  <figure class="card bg-base-100 w-4/5 mx-auto my-12 shadow-xl">
    <div class="card-body">  
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Demos</h1>
      <p class="mb-4">Explore our collection of interactive demos showcasing the capabilities of modern web technologies. Each demo is designed to provide hands-on experience and demonstrate practical applications of various programming concepts.</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
        <li>Real-time Data Visualization</li>
        <li>Interactive UI Components</li>
        <li>Performance Optimization Techniques</li>
        <li>Responsive Design Examples</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">Dive in and experiment with the demos to gain a deeper understanding of how these technologies can be leveraged in your own projects.</p>
    </div>
  </figure>
</Layout>
